{"id":27225,"date":"2020-06-09T13:16:43","date_gmt":"2020-06-09T06:16:43","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=27225"},"modified":"2020-07-01T09:31:18","modified_gmt":"2020-07-01T02:31:18","slug":"huong-dan-cai-dat-thong-bao-wordpress-bang-slack","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/wordpress\/huong-dan-cai-dat-thong-bao-wordpress-bang-slack","title":{"rendered":"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o WordPress t\u1ee9c th\u00ec b\u1eb1ng Slack chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\"><strong>C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o WordPress<\/strong> c\u00e0ng chi ti\u1ebft bao nhi\u00eau th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd website c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1ea5y nhi\u00eau, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m c\u00f9ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd m\u1ed9t hay nhi\u1ec1u website.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 g\u1eedi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o email cho duy nh\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a website v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 website l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f4i khi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u00eam n\u1eefa, email th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady b\u1edfi v\u00ec WordPress d\u00f9ng PHP mail m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n \u0111i v\u00e0o h\u1ed9p th\u01b0 SPAM c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n SMTP \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eedi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c email v\u00e0o h\u1ed9p th\u01b0 th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c s\u00e0n l\u1ecdc, s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp, g\u1eafn nh\u00e3n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec \u0111a s\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3 tr\u00f4i lu\u00f4n. Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 website, v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd th\u00ec l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o n\u00e0o t\u1eeb WordPress tr\u1eeb khi b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng chung Shared Mailbox ho\u1eb7c Email Forwarding.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u00f3i th\u1eadt, b\u1ea1n qu\u00ean email forwarding \u0111i b\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 r\u1eddm r\u00e0, kh\u00f4ng linh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 Gmail lu\u00f4n ch\u1eb7n ho\u1eb7c b\u1eaft b\u1ea1n x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c t\u1eebng mailbox m\u1ed9t. C\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 l\u1ec1 m\u1ec1.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f2n Shared Mailbox (h\u1ed9p mail d\u00f9ng chung) th\u00ec th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 giao ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n c\u00f4ng x\u1eed l\u00fd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t C\u1ef0C H\u00ccNH. Ch\u1ec9 khi b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cao c\u1ea5p \u1edf Shared Mailbox th\u00ec c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng chi ph\u00ed l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u00ec v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd r\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u1ef1 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd website hay theo \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00f3m l\u00e0 d\u00f9ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/slack.com\/intl\/en-vn\/\" target=\"_blank\">Slack<\/a> cho WordPress. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u1eefu \u00edch n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng WooCommerce \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Slack m\u1ea1nh trong qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o theo th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c l\u1ea1i mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 d\u1ea1ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o n\u00e0y \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u. H\u00e3y b\u1ecf t\u00fai tuy\u1ec7t k\u1ef9 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 d\u00f9ng cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">T\u1ea1o k\u00eanh th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Slack cho m\u1ed7i website<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-medium\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"517\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Windows-Slack-client-for-media-kit.en-IN-2x-1201x886-531d543-700x517.png\" alt=\"Windows Slack Client For Media Kit.en In 2x 1201x886 531d543\" class=\"wp-image-27231\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Windows-Slack-client-for-media-kit.en-IN-2x-1201x886-531d543-700x517.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Windows-Slack-client-for-media-kit.en-IN-2x-1201x886-531d543-300x222.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Windows-Slack-client-for-media-kit.en-IN-2x-1201x886-531d543-768x567.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Windows-Slack-client-for-media-kit.en-IN-2x-1201x886-531d543-1024x756.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Windows-Slack-client-for-media-kit.en-IN-2x-1201x886-531d543-218x161.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Windows-Slack-client-for-media-kit.en-IN-2x-1201x886-531d543.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Slack mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n workspaces cho t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1eebng website cho c\u00e1c k\u00eanh th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o kh\u00e1c nhau t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi t\u1eebng t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n kh\u00e1c nhau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1ed9p chung n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfi chuy\u1ec3n qua chuy\u1ec3n l\u1ea1i. R\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Slack g\u00f3i mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed ch\u1ec9 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng apps v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00ean trong m\u1ed7i Workspace (sub-domain c\u1ee7a Slack) c\u00e1i m\u00e0 h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ea1ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o n\u00e0y n\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m. D\u01b0 d\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Slack th\u00ec c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng lo, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Slack b\u1eb1ng clip b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n th\u00ec <a href=\"https:\/\/slack.com\/get-started#\/create\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">\u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Slack m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video alignwide\"><video controls src=\"https:\/\/media.cuongthach.com\/file\/CuongThach\/tao-tai-khoan-slack-moi.mp4\"><\/video><figcaption>\u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd m\u1edbi t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Slack<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1eddi th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00f3m m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh website (tham gia v\u00e0o workspace). B\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p quy\u1ec1n theo d\u00f5i cho t\u1eebng k\u00eanh ri\u00eang l\u1ebd (Slack channel) n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n thay v\u00ec to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 Workspace.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Slack th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f9ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00f3m hay c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 vua trong vi\u1ec7c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c b\u1edfi v\u00ec \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng di \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Slack c\u1ef1c m\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p. Li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch hay g\u1eedi b\u00e1o c\u00e1o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Slack cho WordPress<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u1eedi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Slack n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t plugin mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi l\u00e0 <strong>Slack Notification by dorzki<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"suki-oembed\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"QHCKXqadcl\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/plugins\/dorzki-notifications-to-slack\/\">Slack Notifications by dorzki<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"&#8220;Slack Notifications by dorzki&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" src=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/plugins\/dorzki-notifications-to-slack\/embed\/#?secret=QHCKXqadcl\" data-secret=\"QHCKXqadcl\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o g\u00ec. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng WordPress cho vi\u1ebft blog th\u00f4i th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c k\u00eanh th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>C\u00f3 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn m\u1edbi<\/li><li>\u0110\u0103ng nh\u1eadp Admin Login th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng site \u0111ang b\u1ecb t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng)<\/li><li>WordPres c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n m\u1edbi<\/li><li>Theme c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt m\u1edbi<\/li><li>Plugin c\u00f3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt m\u1edbi<\/li><li>C\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n qua form li\u00ean h\u1ec7<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng b\u1eb1ng WooCommerce th\u00ec b\u1ea1n ch\u00fa \u00fd ch\u00e8n th\u00eam c\u00e1c k\u00eanh th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>C\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng m\u1edbi<\/li><li>T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng (\u0111ang x\u1eed l\u00fd, \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh,&#8230;)<\/li><li>T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n kho<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft l\u1ea1i, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o trong Slack m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 k\u00eanh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o WordPress.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Slack-channels.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Slack-channels-1024x576.png\" alt=\"Slack Channels\" class=\"wp-image-27244\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Slack-channels-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Slack-channels-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Slack-channels-700x394.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Slack-channels-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Slack-channels-218x123.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Slack-channels.png 1854w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>K\u00ean th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Slack cho b\u1ea1n tham kh\u1ea3o<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Xong, ti\u1ebfp theo b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i Slack v\u00e0 WordPress b\u1eb1ng <strong>Incoming Webhook App<\/strong> c\u1ee7a Slack.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video alignwide\"><video controls src=\"https:\/\/media.cuongthach.com\/file\/CuongThach\/tao-webhook-URL-Slack-App.mp4\"><\/video><figcaption>C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t Incoming Webhook App cho k\u00eanh Slack c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Cai-dat-Webhook-URL-Slack.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"594\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Cai-dat-Webhook-URL-Slack-1024x594.png\" alt=\"Cai Dat Webhook Url Slack\" class=\"wp-image-27251\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Cai-dat-Webhook-URL-Slack-1024x594.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Cai-dat-Webhook-URL-Slack-300x174.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Cai-dat-Webhook-URL-Slack-700x406.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Cai-dat-Webhook-URL-Slack-768x445.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Cai-dat-Webhook-URL-Slack-218x126.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Cai-dat-Webhook-URL-Slack.png 1375w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh trong General<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi k\u00eanh Slack t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Tao-Notification-voi-Slack.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"711\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Tao-Notification-voi-Slack-1024x711.png\" alt=\"Tao Notification Voi Slack\" class=\"wp-image-27250\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-cont