eeb Contact Form 7 (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Woocommerce-thong-bao-slack.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"913\" height=\"810\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Woocommerce-thong-bao-slack.png\" alt=\"Woocommerce Thong Bao Slack\" class=\"wp-image-27254\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Woocommerce-thong-bao-slack.png 913w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Woocommerce-thong-bao-slack-300x266.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Woocommerce-thong-bao-slack-700x621.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Woocommerce-thong-bao-slack-768x681.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Woocommerce-thong-bao-slack-218x193.png 218w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 913px) 100vw, 913px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u00e1ch th\u00eam th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Slack WooCommerce<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00e2y gi\u1edd b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ng\u1ed3i ch\u1edd th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c m\u00e1y t\u00ednh v\u1edbi \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Slack m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Noi-dung-thong-bao-khi-co-binh-luan-moi.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"516\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Noi-dung-thong-bao-khi-co-binh-luan-moi-1024x516.png\" alt=\"Noi Dung Thong Bao Khi Co Binh Luan Moi\" class=\"wp-image-27256\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Noi-dung-thong-bao-khi-co-binh-luan-moi-1024x516.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Noi-dung-thong-bao-khi-co-binh-luan-moi-300x151.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Noi-dung-thong-bao-khi-co-binh-luan-moi-700x353.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Noi-dung-thong-bao-khi-co-binh-luan-moi-768x387.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Noi-dung-thong-bao-khi-co-binh-luan-moi-218x110.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Noi-dung-thong-bao-khi-co-binh-luan-moi.png 1922w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>N\u1ed9i dung b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c (b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh) cho m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Slack<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Slack c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean Android, iOS, Mac v\u00e0 Window, b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o ch\u1ee3 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Android-Home.png\" alt=\"Android Home\" class=\"wp-image-27237\" width=\"329\" height=\"601\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Android-Home.png 329w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Android-Home-164x300.png 164w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Android-Home-218x398.png 218w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 329px) 100vw, 329px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o b\u1eb1ng Slack c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 plugin hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng cho ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda n\u1ed9i dung th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o nh\u01b0ng \u1edf b\u1ea3n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u1edbn k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00f3m hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n theo k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng import v\u00e0 export m\u1eabu n\u1ed9i dung th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o cho b\u1ea1n \u0111em qua m\u1ecdi website kh\u00e1c nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1c d\u1ea1ng custom post t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 WooCommerce \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 n\u00ean s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi plugin kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i chia s\u1ebb \u1edf tr\u00ean.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>D\u00f9 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Slack ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o email g\u1eedi b\u1eb1ng SMTP v\u00ec email SMTP c\u00f2n d\u00f9ng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng hay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng song song c\u1ea3 hai l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>N\u1ebfu trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea1n g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn nh\u00e9!<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o WordPress th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c b\u1eb1ng Slack c\u1ef1c h\u1eefu \u00edch khi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u00f3m c\u00f9ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd m\u1ed9t hay nhi\u1ec1u website h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o b\u1eb1ng email.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":27229,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[42],"tags":[46],"featured_image_urls":{"full":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/huong-dan-cai-dat-thong-bao-wordpress-bang-slack.png",1024,512,false],"thumbnail":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/huong-dan-cai-dat-thong-bao-wordpress-bang-slack-300x150.png",270,135,true],"medium":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/huong-dan-cai-dat-thong-bao-wordpress-bang-